OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Food poverty campaigner and chef Jack  
OL,6, Monroe has welcomed changes in the     
OL,7, pipeline to how the cost of living is  
OL,8, measured.                              
OL,10,FMs Monroe had complained that everyday 
OL,11,Fessentials were going up in price by   
OL,12,Fmore than the official inflation rate, 
OL,13,Fhitting poorer people hardest.         
OL,15,FBut she said the official way inflation
OL,16,Fis calculated failed to reflect this.  
OL,18,FOn Wednesday, the official statistics  
OL,19,Fbody hit back, saying it was already   
OL,20,Fchanging how it measured prices.       
